The,Heroku,Connect,API,is,an,application,development,platform,and,is,used,to,exchange,data,between,a,Salesforce,organization,and,a,Heroku,Postgres,database,It,can,be,used,to,sync,accounts,and,custom,objects,from,Salesforce,This,REST,API,responds,in,JSON,format,and,uses,OAuth,version,for,authentication,Salesforce,is,based,in,San,Francisco,and,develops,CRM,software